body:
**EDITH LA STAR** born **Mbunwe Edith Yentoh** is a **Cameroonian gospel artist** who created a path for herself via good vocals, professional music and songwriting. 

From doing music for fun, to debuting her first single in 2019, she announced herself as a star everyone should watch out for. Her voice is a show stopper, her personality is unique. 

Hailing from the Northwest Region of Cameroon, Edith la star is a force to reckon with. She is also a member of Christ Embassy. 

Her music is now available on all digital platforms and for more information on this precious jewel, get to her on her social media pages.

**Subscribe now to my YouTube  Channel**\
https://www.youtube.com/QueenEdithLaStar

**Follow Me On  Facebook** https://www.facebook.com/QueenEdithLastar

**Instagram** https://www.instagram.com/_edith_la_star
